      "body" : "@jacobhyphenated, it not having time zone info manifests as inability for its instances to be converted into an instant, unless given a time zone explicitly. However, the <code>now()</code> of it is a &quot;now&quot; in default zone, hense the local part. It&#39;d honestly be better to just name it <code>DateTime</code> and not give it a <code>now()</code>."
