    "body" : "<p>You can do:</p>\n\n<pre><code>timeStamp.toLocalDateTime().toLocalDate();\n</code></pre>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>Note that <code>timestamp.toLocalDateTime()</code> <strong>will use the <code>Clock.systemDefaultZone()</code> time zone to make the conversion.</strong> This may or may not be what you want.</p>\n</blockquote>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
