      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "@AutomatedMike &quot;adds in a timezone and then takes it off again&quot; - the point is not adding and removing a timezone, but rather converting between different notions by using an <b>explicit</b> timezone. This is in contrast to the examples of my previous two comments where a timezone is applied <b>implicitly</b>."
